      {t:"Remove the social layer (no breaks, no hangout, heads down all day) — it becomes just a coworking space", s:{ph:3}},
      {t:"Both would hurt equally — neither works without the other", s:{ph:3}},
      {t:"Honestly I'm not sure — I haven't thought about it that way", s:{ph:0}}
    ]
  },

  { sec:"The Philosophy", multi: false,
