      {t:"The ritual — it gives their week a shape and anchor point", s:{ph:2}}
    ]
  },

  { sec:"The Philosophy", multi: false,
    q:"Someone attends Creative Blocks in Toronto, then visits another city and finds a session there. What should feel identical?",
    hint:"This defines what the brand actually is at its core.",
