      {t:"It's practical — venues aren't always confirmed far in advance", s:{ph:1}},
      {t:"It filters for committed people — if you show up anyway, you're the right person", s:{ph:3}},
      {t:"Honestly it started practically and I haven't decided if it's a brand choice yet", s:{ph:1}}
    ]
  },

  { sec:"The Philosophy", multi: true,
    q:"In an era of AI, automation, and remote-first work — what human need does Creative Blocks actually serve?",
    hint:"This is the deeper 'why'. Pick all that feel true.",
