      {t:"...people work better in the presence of others and that shouldn't require a corporate office", s:{p:3}},
      {t:"...I wanted to create the kind of community I wished existed when I went remote", s:{p:2}},
      {t:"...there's a gap in the market between coworking spaces (expensive) and working alone (isolating)", s:{p:1}}
    ]
  },

