      "You understand that format and community are interdependent — neither works without the other. Now write that down explicitly. It becomes the host training document, the brand manifesto, the content filter.",
      "Crystal clear. You know exactly what Creative Blocks is at its core, why people return, and what must stay identical across cities. This is the foundation for scaling faithfully."
    ]
  },
  {key:"a", label:"Audience Clarity", max:0,
